source:
TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_SEQ_00Qhoterl Pasol would send you on an errand to Slitherbough.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_SEQ_00Règle spéciale:  synchronisation de quête avec limitation de job ou de classe
* Il n'est possible de progresser dans cette quête qu'avec la classe qui a servi à la commencer.

Qhoterl Pasol voudrait vous envoyer en mission à Serpentige.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_TODO_00<tab>Use the fertilizer at the vegetable plots.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_TODO_00<tab>Utiliser <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E90210202 /var> aux endroits indiqués, à Serpentige

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_TODO_02<tab>Deliver the vegetables to Qhoterl Pasol.
TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Thanks to Master Valan's kind introduction, we were able to establish friendly relations with the good folk of Slitherbough.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Grâce à Valan, Qitari nouer liens avec huuumains de Serpentige<var 1D /var>! Gentils gentils huuumains<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>To mark the occasion, we presented them with our special fertilizer. So happy were they with the gift, they asked if they could have more!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>Qhoterl Pasol décider d'offrir <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E90210202 /var> pour maintenir bonnes relations<var 1D /var>! Bons cadeaux faire bons amis<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_002<tab>Oh yes, we now have an arrangement in place where we provide fertilizer to the settlement in exchange for fresh vegetables.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_002<tab>Engrais faire pousser beaucouuup de légumes bien frais<var 1D /var>! Qitari avoir promis ça aux gentils huuumains, et Qitari leur prouver<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_003<tab>If you're not otherwise occupied, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var> <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, would you mind taking some fertilizer and using it on the crops at Slitherbough? When you have finished, please report to a woman named Ersabel.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_003<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> aller à Serpentige et verser engrais deux fois sur champ<var 1D /var>! Ensuite, dire bonjouuur à Ersabel, d'accord<var 1D /var>? Qhoterl Pasol compter sur toi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_ERSABEL_000_010<tab>Qhoterl Pasol sent you to fertilize our crops, did she? My thanks for your trouble.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_ERSABEL_000_010<tab>C'est donc vous que les Qitari ont envoyé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> verser leur engrais sur notre champ, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var><var 1D /var>? À la bonne heure, ça me fait plaisir de vous revoir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_ERSABEL_000_011<tab>I know not how the Qitari make the stuff, but in all my years, I've not seen any fertilizer work as effectively as theirs.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_ERSABEL_000_011<tab>Il faut dire que ce produit est tout simplement ex<var 16 /var>cep<var 16 /var>tion<var 16 /var>nel. Je n'ai jamais vu des légumes pousser aussi vite de ma vie<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_ERSABEL_000_012<tab>It makes our vegetables grow like a charm, and we're all too happy to share the harvest with our Qitari friends. Please see this delivered to them.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_ERSABEL_000_012<tab>Puis-je vous demander de leur remettre <var 33 ((EventItem)) 07F61E902D0202 /var> en guise de re<var 16 /var>mer<var 16 /var>cie<var 16 /var>ment<var 1D /var>? Je suis sûre qu'ils vont se régaler. À très bientôt<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_ERSABEL_000_020<tab>My thanks again for the fertilizer. Please see that the vegetables are delivered to Qhoterl Pasol.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_ERSABEL_000_020<tab>Veuillez remettre <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E902D0202 /var> aux Qitari en guise de re<var 16 /var>mer<var 16 /var>cie<var 16 /var>ment. Je suis sûre qu'ils vont se régaler. À très bientôt<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab>Welcome back, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. May I ask if you have the vegetables?
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var><var 1D /var>! Avoir rapporté délicieux légumes des gentils huuumains<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_031<tab>My, such splendid crops these are, fairly bursting with the land's vitality! They're a blessing from Dalan Himself!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_031<tab>Oooh, beaucouuup de légumes bien frais<var 1D /var>! Qitari vraiment être bénis par Ox'Dalan<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_032<tab>Everyone will be overjoyed for this treat─my dear husband not least of all!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ105_03810_QHOTERLPASOL_000_032<tab>Mari de Qhoterl Pasol préférer viande bien juteuse, mais quand voir gros légumes, content content quand même<var 1D /var>!
